            <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Key Performance Indicators:</h4>
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-sm text-gray-700">
              <li><strong>Revenue Metrics:</strong> Monthly affiliate earnings, growth rate</li>
              <li><strong>Traffic Metrics:</strong> Organic traffic, conversion rates</li>
              <li><strong>Engagement Metrics:</strong> Email subscribers, community activity</li>
              <li><strong>Operational Metrics:</strong> Content output, response times</li>
              <li><strong>ROI Metrics:</strong> Ad spend efficiency, customer acquisition cost</li>
