                <li><strong>Revenue:</strong> 50% growth in affiliate earnings</li>
                <li><strong>Traffic:</strong> 10,000 monthly organic visitors</li>
                <li><strong>Community:</strong> 1,000 Discord members</li>
                <li><strong>Content:</strong> 20 blog posts published</li>
